                            <comment id="13154513" author="gsingers" created="Mon, 21 Nov 2011 21:10:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks fine, other than it seems like a bit of overkill to have LoadStats and LoadStatsImpl.  Do you envision other implementations?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13154543" author="srowen" created="Mon, 21 Nov 2011 21:23:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah, it was for symmetry with the IRStatistics I suppose, but that&apos;s nearly as much overkill. I can just make it return a simple class and be done.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
